t/tooltip#value-formatting","content":"**Custom:** Pass `formatValue` to control display. The function receives the datum and returns a string. Use it to both extract and format (e.g. currency, percentage, custom units). For custom data point shapes (generic `TooltipProps<YourDatum>`), you must pass `formatValue` because the default only reads `y`."},"909":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-16","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip#single-series","content":"Basic tooltip with a single series and default formatting."},"910":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-17","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip#multiple-series","content":"Tooltip with multiple series; all series at the same X position are shown together."},"911":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-18","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip#arrow","content":"Use the `showArrow` prop to set whether the tooltip arrow is visible or not."},"912":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip","type":"page","content":"TooltipDismissStrip","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Chart"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip"},"913":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip-0","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip","content":"Internal visx XYChart helper that closes the tooltip when the pointer enters a leading-edge strip over scroll-synced axis chrome"},"914":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip-1","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/tooltip-dismiss-strip#internal-component","content":"Internal Component"},"915":{"id":"/docs/components/char