rted","content":"For use with chart components (not exported)"},"1006":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-2","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#props","content":"Props"},"1007":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-3","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#examples","content":"Examples"},"1008":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-4","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#single-series","content":"Single series"},"1009":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-5","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#multiple-series","content":"Multiple series"},"1010":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-6","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"Wrap your chart (or list) with `ChartColorProvider`; each component that calls `useChartColor()` receives a CSS variable reference. Indices are assigned in an effect at mount, so allocation is safe under React concurrent rendering and StrictMode. Same component instance keeps the same color; colors cycle after the ninth consumer. No need to pass an index—order in the tree determines assignment."},"1011":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-7","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#single-series","content":"One series using the first chart color."},"1012":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color-8","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-chart-color#multiple-series","content":"Multiple series each receiving the next color in sequence."},"1013":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","type":"page","content":"useNormalizedSeries","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Chart"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series"},"1014":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series-0","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","content":"A hook that ensures every series config has a stable unique id, generating one from useId when omitted."},"1015":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series-1","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"For use with chart components (not exported)"},"1016":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series-2","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-normalized-series#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"Accepts a `SeriesConfig[]` array and returns a memoized copy where each item is guaranteed to have an `id`. When an item has no `id`, one is generated using a component-scoped prefix from React's `useId`, ensuring IDs are unique across multiple chart instances on the same page. Existing `id` values are preserved as-is."},"1017":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","type":"page","content":"useScrollableXYChart","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Chart"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart"},"1018":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-0","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","content":"A hook for scrollable visx XY charts that measures the rendered axes and returns margins, content-sized width and height, scroll offsets, and a vertical-labels flag, so the chart sizes itself to whatever it actually contains."},"1019":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-1","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"For use with chart components (not exported)"},"1020":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-2","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#examples","content":"Examples"},"1021":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-3","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#auto-layout","content":"Auto layout"},"1022":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-4","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"**Inputs.** Wire `parentRef` to the scroll container and `xAxisRef` / `yAxisRef` to the axis groups. Optionally pass `xLabelsOrientation` (`'auto'` | `'horizontal'` | `'vertical'`, default `'auto'`) to force the category-label layout; `'auto'` rotates labels vertical when the visible width can't fit the horizontal-tick footprint plus the Y-axis width."},"1023":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-5","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"**Outputs.** The hook returns `margin`, `chartWidth`, `chartHeight`, `xLabelsVertical`, `scrollLeft` / `scrollTop`, and `yAxisRect` for the chart to consume. Width and height are sized to whichever is larger — the visible slot or the room the rendered labels need — so the chart grows past the viewport and the parent scrolls when labels demand more space."},"1024":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-6","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#for-use-with-chart-components-not-exported","content":"**Behavior.** Measurement runs through `useParentSize`, a `MutationObserver`, and a `ResizeObserver` on the wired nodes. All axis measurements are batched in one `requestAnimationFrame` and bail out when the result hasn't changed, so a burst of observer fires costs at most one reflow and one render per frame."},"1025":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart-7","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/use-scrollable-xy-chart#auto-layout","content":"Hook wired to a scrolling parent; scroll or resize to watch the returned values update."},"1026":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","type":"page","content":"Box","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components","Layout"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/layout/box"},"1027":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-0","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/layout/box","content":"Polymorphic layout component providing consistent spacing, elevation, rounding, and self-alignment"},"1028":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-1","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/layout/box#installation","content":"Installation"},"1029":{"id":"/docs/components/layout/box-2","page_id":"/docs/components/layout/box","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/layout/box#props","content":"Props"},"1030":{"id":"/docs/components/lay